<div style="position:absolute;left:272.57px;top:120.26px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">DIGIIROBE</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:77.90px;top:163.94px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">DIGIIROBE or Digital Intelligent Wardrobe is a smart IoT device crafted to manage your fashion gear or</span></div>
